title: Disable Line Numbers in Org Mode
tags: @zettel _method emacs orgmode
roam-id: 5ede79c9-372d-47a2-921c-724178b21d02
type: text/markdown

add the following hook in your init.el or config.el

``` elisp
(add-hook 'org-mode-hook (lambda () (display-line-numbers-mode 0))) ;; disable line numbers in org
```
